\begin_layout Solution*
使用散度定理(又称空间Green定理, Gauss公式), 定理的条件在原点
\begin_inset Formula $(0,0,0)$
\end_inset

不满足, 所以考虑挖去原点为心
\begin_inset Formula $\varepsilon$
\end_inset

为半径的球
\begin_inset Formula $\Omega_{\varepsilon}=\{(x,y,z):x^{2}+y^{2}+z^{2}\le\varepsilon^{2}\}$
\end_inset

, 则
\begin_inset Formula $\Sigma$
\end_inset

内
\begin_inset Formula $\partial\Omega_{\varepsilon}$
\end_inset

外的部分总有
\begin_inset Formula $\sumcyc\partial_{x}\frac{x}{r^{3}}=0$
\end_inset

恒成立, 所以
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\iint_{\Sigma}=\iint_{\Sigma-\partial\Omega_{\varepsilon}}+\iint_{\partial\Omega_{\varepsilon}}=\iiint_{\Sigma^{\circ}-\Omega_{\varepsilon}}0\ud x\ud y\ud z+\frac{1}{\varepsilon^{3}}\iint_{\partial\Omega_{\varepsilon}}x\ud y\ud z+y\ud z\ud x+z\ud x\ud y.
\]

\end_inset

而上式对上式右边重积分再用一次散度定理, 便有
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\iint_{\partial\Omega_{\varepsilon}}=\iiint_{\Omega_{\varepsilon}}3\ud x\ud y\ud z=4\pi\varepsilon^{3},
\]

\end_inset

所以最后的结果为
\begin_inset Formula $4\pi$
\end_inset

.
\end_layout

