+\left(-4w+2ux+2wy\right)a^{3}bc+\left(2w-2ux-wx-2wy\right)a^{2}b^{2}c
\end{array}}{\left(2a+b\right)\left(2b+c\right)\left(2c+a\right)}.
\]

\end_inset

所以
\begin_inset Formula $u=1$
\end_inset

, 
\begin_inset Formula $y=4$
\end_inset

